snippet.title: The Strongest TOFU - Trailer
snippet.description: The Strongest TOFU, the ultimate condensed soy milk action platformer from developer Zounoashi Games and publisher Phoenixx, tumbles onto PC via Steam on Japan's Tofu Day, Wednesday, 2 Oct 2024.
